### Seed com header secreto (deve retornar 200 com resumo)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/seed
X-Admin-Secret: codice-seed-dev-secret
Content-Type: application/json

### Seed sem header (deve retornar 403)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/seed
Content-Type: application/json

### Seed com header errado (deve retornar 403)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/seed
X-Admin-Secret: valor-errado
Content-Type: application/json

### Listar books (paginacao default)
GET http://localhost:8080/books

### Listar books (paginacao custom, ordenado por titulo)
GET http://localhost:8080/books?page=0&size=5&sort=title,asc

### Buscar book por slug
GET http://localhost:8080/books/memorias-postumas-de-bras-cubas

### Buscar book por slug inexistente (deve retornar 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/books/slug-que-nao-existe
